  ],
  "remarks": "Vadim Moshkovich is a Russian entrepreneur with business interests in agriculture and real-estate development. In 2004, Vadim Moshkovich founded Rusagro Group, which is a major producer of pork, fats and sugar, rated first among agricultural holdings in 2021 in Russia. Vadim Moshkovich is therefore a businessperson involved in economic sectors providing a substantial source of revenue to the Government of the Russian Federation.",
